Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:47.49,Alternative,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362360,1367490}Therefore, the expected time of arrival to Tōkyō is expected to be greatly delayed.{NOTE:従いまして、東京着の予定時刻は大幅に遅れる見込みです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:22:49.41,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1367490,1369410}Arrival in Tōkyō is delayed?{NOTE:東京着が遅れる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:52.83,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1369410,1372830}But if the typhoon gets worse, we might stop altogether. That's can't happen!{NOTE:でも、このまま台風がひどくなれば、ストップも考えられるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:53.74,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1372830,1373740}What to do?{NOTE:どうしよう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:56.79,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1375790,1376790}This is bad.{NOTE:まずい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:23:02.29,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1376790,1382290}This typhoon… Professor Nakajima told me she'll get on "Kodama", but I'm still worried.{NOTE:この台風…「こだま」に乗ったと伝えてきた、中島先生の切符は逆に不安になってくる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:23:02.29,Sign,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1376790,1382290}Kodama - train service
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:04.42,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1382290,1384420}Professor, time to go.{NOTE:先生、出発の時間です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:07.17,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1385300,1387170}Oh, I will go in a second.{NOTE:あ、今行く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:09.55,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1388130,1389550}We're counting on you, Ayuhara.{NOTE:頼むぞ、鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:17.47,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1395140,1397470}What if the train doesn't make it in time…?{NOTE:まさか、この列車が間に合わなかったら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.47,0:23:20.23,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1397470,1400230}Then all of that work will go to waste.{NOTE:私の今までやってきてくだ全て無駄に成る。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:22.65,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1400230,1402650}My blood, our training, everything will be in vain.{NOTE:血みどろの特訓は皆無駄に成るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:26.44,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1402650,1406440}I can survive losing to Kakinouchi-san in a proper battle.{NOTE:垣之内さんと戦って負けても、私には諦めのXXがあるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.44,0:23:29.32,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1406440,1409320}But if I lose without even being able to put up a fight…{NOTE:でも、戦わない前にこんなことで負けるなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:31.03,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1409320,1411030}I can't handle that.{NOTE:そんなことって絶対に嫌。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.03,0:23:32.57,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1411030,1412570}It's okay. Don't worry.{NOTE:大丈夫だよ。心配ない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:33.70,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1412570,1413700}We'll make it.{NOTE:間に合うとも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:34.66,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1413700,1414660}Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:36.70,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1414990,1416700}Oh, dear God.{NOTE:あ、神様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.70,0:23:39.41,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1416700,1419410}Please let me make it in time for the game.{NOTE:どうか、試合にだけは間に合わせてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:41.79,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1419410,1421790}I do not want to lose without fighting.{NOTE:戦わないで負けるなんて嫌です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.79,0:23:43.75,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1421790,1423750}I'd absolutely hate that.{NOTE:絶対に嫌です。}
