Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:00.60,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1438470,1440600}The audience is watching over…{NOTE:XXXの観衆が見守る中。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:04.06,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1440600,1444060}…as the battle between Fujimi Academy and Fukuoka Middle School begins.{NOTE:富士見学園と福岡中学の熱戦が展開している。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.06,0:24:07.82,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1444060,1447820}Kakinouchi's intense spike hits the Fujimi team's side again and again.{NOTE:垣之内の強烈なスパイクがまたもや富士見コートに決まる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.82,0:24:12.40,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1447820,1452400}Fujimi Academy is on the defensive.\NIt seems that the outcome is already decided.{NOTE:防戦一方の富士見学園すでに優勝の行方は決まったかに見える。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.40,0:24:18.20,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1452400,1458200}Meanwhile, the typhoon becomes even stronger and Kozue's train drops its speed again.{NOTE:その頃、台風の勢いはさらに強まりこずえの乗ったひかり号はまたもスピードを落とした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.20,0:24:19.95,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1458200,1459950}Will she make it in time for the game?{NOTE:試合に間に合うのだろうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.95,0:24:23.58,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1459950,1463580}Please look forward to the next episode.{NOTE:さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンはお楽しみに。}
